{"tid":1358231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"搞港鐵有乜用, 直接受害係普通人, 港鐵冇損失","createTime":"2019-07-24T01:27:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T04:29:13.000Z","uid":64743,"like":24,"dislike":118,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"4334ff08506f5ffbea8f73834cabe6ff31893220","tid":1358231,"uid":64743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:27:32.000Z","msg":"1. 我地係要爭取普通人支持走落去, 唔係搞到啲人<br />\n2. 你咁樣唔比閂門, 唔比架車開, 你咪做緊一班白衫佬既野囉, 直接受害係普通人, 港鐵冇損失架<br />\n3. 你要搞, 就發起全港跳閘塔車, 唔比車錢, 然後上到車箱舉叫人一齊唔好比錢車, 叫人支持, 大把人舉腳讚承啦, 咁樣港鐵先會有直接損失"},{"pid":"43392d7dadc0b4fd637b5a5a8dff3d2c3e61c1bd","tid":1358231,"uid":64743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:30:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"67d18efce3c34ae58c5e44d9e024e68828786e75","tid":1358231,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:30:34.000Z","msg":"同意唔撚比錢"},{"pid":"79c36fc116aef744816a5278c15bf0b73a0005f7","tid":1358231,"uid":145600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:31:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"369f8d9ce8eae73452013cd51a2ac60d16fcfb89","tid":1358231,"uid":64743,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:32:07.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n負皮果啲, 講下原因好喎"},{"pid":"9176f5694237a5b317634110ea6e3562f64db1e3","tid":1358231,"uid":273716,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:34:35.000Z","msg":"我今日都要番工<br />\n知道今日塞地鐵<br />\n我就知遲硬到所以慢慢行<br />\n反正大條道理遲到<br />\n我輕輕鬆鬆出門口番工不知幾開心<br />\n打工仔表示好支持，差啲想塞埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人嘈既就心平氣和同佢解釋星期日狗鐵做左咩事<br />\n好好文宣機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80156907ee052de636543765590013bab8dcadac","tid":1358231,"uid":64743,"like":0,"dislike":